Package JUnit4Tests

Class XMLTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • JUnit4Tests.XMLTest
  • public class XMLTest
extends java.lang.Object
    JUnit4 Test Cases for DatabaseHandler and subclasses Notes: For every test case, a new user file is generated, to prevent issues in other tests. Considering moving to @before, but some test cases could be designed around that, so it's left open. Just be careful when adding test cases.
